channel.title: Removing IP
channel.description: Hi, im having this problem. When i open client.java on my client, i removed the IP address so you can see it when you are logging in but its connecting to a specific server (in this case my server) the problem is that if you press ENTER you will go to the password field, if you press ENTER again you will go to the ip field even though its not there, and you can still change the ip address it connects to. How do i make it so when hes in the password field and presses enter he goes back to the username field instad of the invisible ip field.
